| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5211 — Recovery Inhibition (snatch)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f2bb23e3-b2c9-5bb1-a4fc-e425d15618ca"
